Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After leaving the fateful island, Dressrosa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others headed \Nfor the unknown island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:24.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Zou, following Nami and \Nthe others who went ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the island, Zou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy! But this is a {\i1}zou{\i0} (elephant)!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Zou is the name of a place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that flourishes on the back \Nof a massive elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The New Warlord!\NThe Legendary Whitebeard's Son Appears!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! D-D-Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the grand ship that carries\Nthe sacred bodies of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thousand Sunny-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!\NI feel blessed! I feel blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worship it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! So they made it to Zou for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they got away from Big Mom nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no major damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Chopper! Brook! Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what was the gas guy's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?!\N--The elephant's leg is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keep up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier-bility: Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the leg on the other side is\Nabout to move forward now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one will move again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you {\i1}senpai{\i0}, hurry up and cross over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're already crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Have you seen the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they all made landfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's catch up to them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take care, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY'S GENERAL HEADQUARTERS\NBALTIGO, GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebel armies are winning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,all across the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:42.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MONKEY D. DRAGON\NTHE GENERAL COMMANDER\N OF THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The fall of the Donquixote Family
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:48.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,had a huge impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This many countries were involved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:53.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,in the weapon trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war situation is looking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But tell them not to be too \Nexcited over their win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government won't \Njust sit by quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cipher Pol has been \Nreinforced in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell them to take extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they found a \Nspecial ore in the weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we brought back from Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of Drunken Iron Ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite rare\Nand only a few countries can mine it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they might be able to figure out\Nwhere the weapons were actually made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought back our people who \Nwent missing in Dressrosa too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing remarkably well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I couldn't do it\Nwithout Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she was caught in Sabaody\Nbut that was completely false.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was! She was totally full of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna ask me about Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've had more than enough with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I bet Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0} told you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon all the leaders of the Revolutionary \NArmy from all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Do you really wanna summon\Nall those big personalities again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:34.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A SEA SOMEWHERE IN THE NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lafitte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This... urgess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Burgess! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:56.78,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"DEMON SHERIFF" LAFITTE\NTHE CAPTAIN OF THE FIFTH SHIP OF\NTHE EMPEROR - BLACKBEARD'S PIRATE GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to Dressrosa to pick you up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,but you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't make contact since I was \Nunconscious almost the whole time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.50,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIRYU OF THE RAIN\NTHE CAPTAIN OF THE SECOND SHIP OF\NTHE EMPEROR - BLACKBEARD'S PIRATE GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:12.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that son of a gun was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all white...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an island as white as snow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hiding in the bottom of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Captain Teech!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we invade here now, we can \Nget a massive amount of weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Commodore Teech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to bring Doc Q too!\NI'm fatally injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burgess! Tell us already! Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the name of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a totally uncharted place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Follow my Vivre Card and come here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon and the obnoxious Sabo are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Revolutionary Army's \Ngeneral headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:27.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AN ISLAND SOMEWHERE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so dumb and ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all say the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the members of the Whitebeard Pirates\Nare Whitebeard's only sons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:44.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EDWARD WEEVIL - A WARLORD\NSELF-PROCLAIMED "WHITEBEARD JR."\N(FORMER BOUNTY: 480 MILLION BERRIES)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:50.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard's son, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My beard's white as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates were \Njust a make-believe family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only biological son of\Nthe world's strongest pirate, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MISS BUCKIN - WEEVIL'S MOTHER\NSELF-PROCLAIMED "WHITEBEARD'S LOVER"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:17.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman who Whitebeard loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hold your head up, my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting me, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look at this!\N--What? Is that a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a picture of Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought that was a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so much like him - there's \Nno way you're not his son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so silly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!\NSay what you've got to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the remnants of the Whitebeard Pirates\Nlike Marco the Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And get something back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father Newgate must've left\Nbehind a big fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're the true heir\Nsince you're his biological son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! But what I really \Nwanna do is get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna have my revenge on \NBlackbeard for killing Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive him at any price!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly boy! What's the \Npoint in taking revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even earn one berry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want money!\NYou must inherit his fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him again! Garp's grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Marco and the others tried \Nto protect him in the Paramount War.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe he knows something about Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go beat him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:49.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"BUGGY TOWN"\NEMPTEE BLUFFS ISLAND, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:57.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BUGGY'S DELIVERY - A PIRATE MERCENARY AGENCY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hello, hello?\N--{\i1}Do you still have the one from the other day?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, we do!\N--Hi! Thank you for calling Buggy's Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We need one in a hurry! It's very urgent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Director Buggy!\N--What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep getting orders\Nand the Snails won't stop ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they can't get weapons\Nfrom Doflamingo now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they turned to pirate mercenaries\Nand we're getting a flood of calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We reign supreme over the military market!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever finishes eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go to battlefields and run \Nwild, and bring back booty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:44.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BUGGY THE GENIUS JESTER - A WARLORD/PIRATE\NTHE DIRECTOR OF BUGGY'S DELIVERY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pirating is legitimate \Nunder the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:55.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Warlord - Buggy \Nthe Genius Jester-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Director Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you we got a call from\Nthe S-class mercenary, Hajrudin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said he wants to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just one Giant - let it go.\NWe have four others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, all five of them want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're our biggest earners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're so busy now!\N I wanna know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't wanna hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you {\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We moved all our food to your ship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think you're gonna be okay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else that you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could follow them and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,see all the stars of the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from my dreams for even a little while but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't wanna get in the way of\Nthe adventures of those gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our happiness barometer is\Nalready at full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll all have abilities that \Nare worthy of being called
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,subordinates of the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we can help you at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,we want the four other {\i1}senpai{\i0}'s Divine Drops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE DIVINE DROPS (AUTOGRAPHS)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:40.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a sheer pleasure \Nif we can have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that an earthworm?\N--It's a snake, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has legs so it's a lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally ignoring me!\NComplete disregard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy even with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this?\N--I still think it's a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that a snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Rising Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's gonna say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of pathetic creature appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why did you...?\N--Like they say, an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cute...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cute...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we can fly on the dragon,\Nwe can get there quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone, cling to its back!\NIt's gonna climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it gonna fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Keep going, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many kilometers to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no end up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure there's a country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vivre Card is pointing upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Dragon! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}! I'll look \Nforward to seeing you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Bartolomeo will devote myself every day\Nto becoming a fine pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To becoming a fine pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Bartolomeo and the \Nothers are saying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lome-o, huh?\NI forgot to even thank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Lome-o, it's Lomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lome-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Lome-o and everybody!\NThank you for bringing us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did he just call my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He called my name for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care on your journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:49.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-senpai! Take care!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:57.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, the party keeps climbing up to \Nthe top of the Phantom Island, Zou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:13.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To meet up with Sanji and the \Nothers, Luffy and his group
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:17.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,head for the massive elephant's \Nback in the far distance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:19.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After climbing up the steep cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and overcoming a number of crises \Nand a heartbreaking goodbye,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:26.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Phantom Island that's wrapped in a mystery\Nfinally shows itself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Deadly Elephant Climb!\NA Great Adventure on the Back of the Giant Elephant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
